rows.label: tlk42400045_03_msg0001
rows.name: Tolulu have new employer called Ion.

rows.label: tlk42400045_03_msg0002
rows.name:
Tolulu met Ion while playing on
waterway flume by Great Stairway.
Not much else to do while unemployed.

rows.label: tlk42400045_03_msg0003
rows.name:
But it turn out, being ticket-collector at
Bajena Playhouse actually lot of fun!

rows.label: tlk42400045_03_msg0004
rows.name:
Only downside is that wages come out
of Ion's pocket money and that make
Tolulu feel bad...
